name: Silent Observer
description:
Silent Observer is about the quiet ones. The ones who'd rather take to the background and watch than speak out. 

But watch they do. 

Original Medium: Color pencil

Art: Smileymaste (smileymaste.com)
3D/AR: KilljoyInk (killjoyink.tez)

Collaborative piece.
